description:
Hi everyone! I have decided to launch this [weekly team battle](https://lichess.org/forum/team-world-classicals/weekly-world-classicals-team-battle) for Classical Chess lovers. It lasts 12h to give each of you a chance to play whenever you can, each Saturday.

Good luck and have fun!

[Ivan Gabriele](https://lichess.org/@/Ivan_Gabriele)
